This paper involves the use of deep learning for image analysis and localization, which is a common theme in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and robotics (cs.RO) in the context of medical imaging. Additionally, the paper involves the use of image processing techniques (cs.MM) to improve the accuracy of the localization algorithm.
